                                        Table "public.schools"
   Column   |            Type             | Collation | Nullable |               Default               
------------+-----------------------------+-----------+----------+-------------------------------------
 id         | bigint                      |           | not null | nextval('schools_id_seq'::regclass)
 name       | character varying(255)      |           | not null | 
 code       | character varying(50)       |           | not null | 
 address    | text                        |           |          | 
 phone      | character varying(50)       |           |          | NULL::character varying
 email      | character varying(100)      |           |          | NULL::character varying
 website    | character varying(100)      |           |          | NULL::character varying
 status     | school_status               |           |          | 'active'::school_status
 created_at | timestamp without time zone |           |          | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
 updated_at | timestamp without time zone |           |          | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
Indexes:
    "schools_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "idx_schools_code" btree (code)
    "idx_schools_status" btree (status)
    "schools_code_key" UNIQUE CONSTRAINT, btree (code)
